Meet <b>LeTanya Ashante</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>LeTanya Ashante lives at <a href='/home/?user=babyblue333'>14557 Young Street</a> in the trendy neighborhood of Metro Park.  LeTanya Ashante loves living in Metro Park because it puts her within easy walking distance of <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/main_map.phtml?location=downtown">Downtown Millsberry</a>'s shops.  She has taken many shopping trips to browse and buy in the Downtown area since moving to Millsberry on November 10, 2004.<br><br>LeTanya Ashante prides herself on being a well-rounded person.  She thinks it's very beneficial to develop every aspect of her personality and have a variety of interests, from academics and athletics to art.  LeTanya Ashante spends her weekdays at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a>, where she quickly shot to the top of her class.  Her favorite subject is astronomy, and in addition to being a member of the Astronomy Society, LeTanya Ashante recently started her own astronomy club with her best friend.  Every weekend, LeTanya Ashante takes her special silver, yellow, and black telescope over to her best friend's house, where they spend the evening scanning the stars above Millsberry.<br><br>It's not all work and no play for LeTanya Ashante, though!  After school and on weekends, she can often be found practicing with her soccer team in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park/">Peabody Park</a>.  LeTanya Ashante loves to dribble the ball across the field, stutter-stepping past her opponents as she heads toward the goal to blast a kick past the goalkeeper.  If her team doesn't have a game that day, LeTanya Ashante is usually an active spectator, cheering on her favorite teams and players to victory.<br><br>LeTanya Ashante is able to indulge her artistic side through her love of music.  She finds that it's the easiest and most fun way for her to express herself.  LeTanya Ashante recently dropped by the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/studio/">Millsberry Recording Studio</a> to share her musical appreciation with her fellow citizens.  Her songs are rhythmic, fast-paced, and inspired by her favorite styles of music - rhythm & blues, rap, and punk.  Her upbeat tunes have caught the attention of many Millsberry residents, and one of her songs even coasted to the top of the Cinnamon Toast Crunch Top Ten charts!<br><br>Thank you for being a fine citizen, LeTanya Ashante, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
